Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:12.72,Default,2,0,0,0,,We're back. {ep 18}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.04,San,San,0,0,0,,Welcome back. {ep 18}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:16.80,San,San,0,0,0,,Was the trip fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:17.59,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.59,0:00:20.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san. Please go on a date with me next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:21.05,San,San,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:24.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, you broke your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:27.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was so looking forward to going on a trip with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:30.01,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop hitting on someone else's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:31.74,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Akki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:34.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio, of course you'll be coming with us on the date.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:35.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:35.91,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:37.73,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Then let me come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:41.34,San,San,0,0,0,,Let's have a good time with just\Nthe three of us, Tomoya-san, Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.34,0:00:43.62,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don't leave me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:12.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:15.28,San,San,0,0,0,,Tomoya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:19.98,San,San,0,0,0,,It hasn't changed, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:24.77,San,San,0,0,0,,I've left it just the way it was on the day she married you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:26.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes, it hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:29.97,San,San,0,0,0,,Would you like to take those with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:32.22,San,San,0,0,0,,Those dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.81,0:01:34.86,San,San,0,0,0,,Ushio loves them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:41.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:41.90,San,San,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:44.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I forced Ushio on you for all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:51.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's thanks to you I was able to realize that I'm a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.41,San,San,0,0,0,,I haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:57.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's a really good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:01:59.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don't know how to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:02.23,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,All right, next up is the imitation of Mikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:03.52,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Mikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:08.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But starting today, I will raise her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:12.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I will raise her to be a strong and caring person like Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:20.50,San,San,0,0,0,,When we changed our occupations for Nagisa, she was also five years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:22.77,San,San,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:26.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I will spend the rest of my life to repay my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:30.05,San,San,0,0,0,,Then please have a wonderful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:34.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:35.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Together with Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:36.77,San,San,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:39.24,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:44.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's up, Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:46.76,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Akki said let's play baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:47.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:50.33,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:52.39,San,San,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.39,0:02:57.41,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,A guy that used to have eyes of a dead fish is up and about. {ep 18}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:59.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Shut up and throw it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:03.84,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Ushio! Observe your father's pathetic look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:04.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:07.34,San,San,0,0,0,,Who do you think will win, Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:08.24,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Akki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:09.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:13.12,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,She grew up seeing my great arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:16.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then I'll just hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:18.04,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Bull crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:28.07,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,See that, Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:30.29,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:34.76,San,San,0,0,0,,Looks like we have to go apologize again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:22.82,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Episode 19
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:22.82,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}Homeward Bound
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:37.63,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Sanae, you're not one to talk about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.63,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You haven't cried since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.25,San,San,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:48.56,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Of course. Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:52.00,San,San,0,0,0,,Well, I had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:55.55,San,San,0,0,0,,I had to raise Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:06:01.49,San,San,0,0,0,,So it was good; I didn't have the chance to lose myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.81,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Five years, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:07.32,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We were saved by Ushio a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.88,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:13.01,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But even that has come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:14.53,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.84,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Good work for many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.67,San,San,0,0,0,,It was nothing; we're a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:27.22,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's all right, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.62,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.87,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:34.98,San,San,0,0,0,,Akio-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:38.36,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Even with all hope gone, I'll still help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:41.23,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I'll be here until you stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:43.61,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So it's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:17.23,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:18.67,San,San,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:20.60,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Yeah, go and score!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:21.20,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You understand what he means?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:27.31,San,San,0,0,0,,You'll get to live with your father starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:28.87,San,San,0,0,0,,Be sure to be a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:29.82,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:35.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,On days I'm busy with work, can I still ask you to take her to or pick her up from kindergarten?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:37.53,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Sure, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:40.29,San,San,0,0,0,,Tomoya-san, how about your...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I intend to visit him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:53.22,Default,Princ,0,0,0,,I heard the particulars from Furukawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:56.28,Default,Princ,0,0,0,,It's nice meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Same here. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:03.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right then, Ushio. Daddy's off to work, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:05.67,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup. Have a good day, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:16.97,Default,People,0,0,0,,Look. That's Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.85,Default,People,0,0,0,,I wonder what he was doing all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:22.18,Default,People,0,0,0,,Did something happen with the Furukawas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.00,Default,People,0,0,0,,Family dispute, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:25.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I bet I would have snapped if this had happened a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:28.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:31.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm Okazaki Ushio's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.57,Default,People,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:38.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I've been leaving her at my wife's home due to circumstances beyond my control,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:41.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,but we'll be living together starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I hope we'll get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:46.22,Default,People,0,0,0,,Oh, same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:50.16,Default,People,0,0,0,,My child's a good friend of Ushio-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:52.11,Default,People,0,0,0,,I hope we'll get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:56.14,Default,Yus,0,0,0,,Really? So you'll be living with her from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:59.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes. Sorry for worrying you for all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:03.33,Default,Yus,0,0,0,,But won't it be hard to raise a small child alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:08.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san and the old man took care of the most critical days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:13.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No matter what I may face, it won't be anything compared to what those two faced.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.50,Default,Yus,0,0,0,,Come to me if you ever need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:20.27,Default,Yus,0,0,0,,The company will try to accommodate you as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:22.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, in that case, something right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.02,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:28.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm here to get you, Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:37.28,Default,Princ,0,0,0,,Right now, it's the summer session,\Nso Ushio-chan's teacher's on holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:39.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Holiday? Sick perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:42.21,Default,Princ,0,0,0,,She's off to a child-care seminar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:47.29,Default,Princ,0,0,0,,She'll be back next week, so you will meet her when she returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:48.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:52.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's your teacher like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:55.39,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Long hair, beautiful, and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:56.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:01.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right, Daddy's going to go back to work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:04.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Even if a stranger comes, don't open the door, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:05.52,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:09.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If anything happens, call Sanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:11.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You know how to make calls, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:12.44,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll be back before dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:16.32,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:17.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:18.82,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Bye-bye,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:19.72,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:47.04,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:51.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's Daddy. My hands are full with stuff;\Nopen the door for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:58.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I brought them from the Furukawas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:02.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The Big Dango Family, your toys, and changes of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:04.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's put this somewhere first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:07.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Where do you think is best?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:13.42,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:15.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right. There it'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:26.01,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Can you cook, Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:28.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll learn little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:30.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We'll learn together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:31.04,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:33.67,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:38.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kouko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:39.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.76,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,I wonder how many years it has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.64,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,So she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,My daughter, Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:47.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio, say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:49.26,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.02,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Yes, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.46,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,I'm Yoshino Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:57.10,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,So she's Nagisa-chan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.86,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,She does resemble her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:06.72,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll grow up to be a strong and cute girl like Nagisa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:09.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I hope so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She used to be Mommy's teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:16.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Yoshino-san told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:18.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I heard your sister got discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:26.49,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Yes. The doctors said it's a miracle,\Nbut we always believed she'd be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:30.19,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,I'm actually with her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:33.91,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Fu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:43.49,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.88,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,They're my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:49.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:02.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What an interesting sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:06.44,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Fu-chan; he's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:08.82,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,This is my younger sister, Fuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:11.95,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,This is Okazaki-san and Ushio-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.74,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:15.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:16.71,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:21.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:23.64,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,She's cute! Can I give her a hug?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:27.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You didn't even wait for an answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.27,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Stop it, Fu-chan. You're being rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:34.75,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. She's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How old is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:39.01,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,The same age as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:45.80,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,But since she's been sleeping all these years, she still thinks she's a freshman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why does she look no different from Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:53.08,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,You're both very rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:57.07,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuko's mad, so Fuko's going to make her Fuko's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:59.59,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Stop saying nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:01.91,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It's not going to fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:02.59,Default,2,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.55,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:14.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She was a little strange, but it was nice that you made a new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.17,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:20.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio, I don't have to go to work tomorrow. Will you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:21.99,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Another trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:23.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:32.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You like the Big Dango Family, too? {ep 18}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:37.02,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Sanae-san said this is how Mommy smelled. {ep 18}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:37.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:39.92,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:00.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm home. {ep 18}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:15:13.26,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}Note: The radio is broadcasting the results of a horserace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:20.79,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Ah, Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:33.93,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:37.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You've gotten old, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:38.44,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:42.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's your granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.27,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:48.53,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:53.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Have you been here all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:55.78,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I met your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:03.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I went on a trip with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Way up north.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:09.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The place you took me once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:13.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I heard a lot of stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:16.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It made me think that you must have been through many hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:21.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I remembered a lot of things from the past, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:26.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:33.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think it's all right for you to rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How about going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Your mother's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:43.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Right where you took my hand and promised to raise me with your own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:51.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You've done enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:54.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So relax now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:58.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Go home and live with your mother for her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:16:59.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:20.37,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Is it... over now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:21.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:25.63,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Have I accomplished it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:41.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You sacrificed everything and raised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:49.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You spent your entire life on a worthless son like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:52.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You've done enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:56.33,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:18:01.68,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,So I managed to do it without even knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:07.67,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:13.34,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:39.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll put a change of clothes and some money in, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:41.57,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:44.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll give her a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:47.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't lose your bags on the way, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:49.46,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:52.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll handle the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:55.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the debts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.59,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:01.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio, say bye-bye to your granddad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.54,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, Granddad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:04.26,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:12.85,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:16.34,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:21.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't drink too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:21.74,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:23.95,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Tomoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.54,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,There, have a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't smoke too much, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.08,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:34.73,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Dad's got to go again, but don't eat too much, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:36.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Live long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:39.34,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Sorry I have to leave you alone all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:42.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll definitely go to show my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:45.98,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'll make our dinner when I come back, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:47.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I will go, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:49.58,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,We'll eat it together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.45,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,All right, Tomoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:06.53,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Tomoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:11.66,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:23.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:26.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:30.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thank you for all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:34.52,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:42.63,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'll go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:46.28,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You, too, Tomoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:21:00.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I wonder if he had a good life or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:08.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He lost his dearest person at the happiest time in his life, and he's been alone with me ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:13.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He kept working for an ungrateful son like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:16.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I wonder if he had a good life like that or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:23.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What is it, Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:53.39,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:55.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, is it bright there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:56.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Come here.
