Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:45.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Ushio. You're going to have a visitor tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:48.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you know any games, Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:51.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio, say "I'm going" to Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:53.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, Ushio!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.83,0:23:55.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's dangerous, so wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.00,0:23:59.62,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.53,0:24:01.87,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Good luck.
