Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.95,0:00:33.83,Kara-Ins,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Like the traces of the heart, no halt at the places.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:45.00,Kara-Ins,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}The place is so far away be far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:58.26,Kara-Ins,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}People's hand does not reach, so merely has the worship.
