Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:23.78,Kara-Ins,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We will lose the place, so lofty which changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:35.64,Kara-Ins,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Not all were desired. However, we're never sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.06,0:01:50.06,Kara-Ins,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Still, there is still the place. Far away. Far away.
